articles.author: Kirsty Needham
articles.title: Australia signs security, migration pact with Pacific's Tuvalu - Reuters
articles.description: Australia announced on Friday a security guarantee to the Pacific Islands nation of Tuvalu to respond to military aggression, protect it from climate change and boost migration in a pact aimed at countering China's influence in the Pacific.
